# Design System Rules

## Tokens first

- Edit colors/spacing in `src/styles/tokens.css`, not in components.
- Use semantic utilities: `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `text-muted-foreground`, `border-border`.
- Layout widths: `max-w-content`, `max-w-content-wide`, `max-w-prose`, `py-section-y`.

## Imports

- `cn` from `@/lib/utils`
- Typography/layout from `@/lib/design-system`
- UI primitives from `@/components/ui/*`
- Site/nav from `@/config/site`, `@/config/navigation`

## Do not

- Hardcode hex/oklch/rgb in TSX
- Duplicate shadcn primitives (custom Button/Card)
- Link nav items with `enabled: false` in `navigation.ts`
- Add `tailwind.config.*` (Tailwind v4 is CSS-first)

## shadcn

- Style: `base-nova` per `components.json`
- Add components: `bunx shadcn@latest add <name> -y`
- Client boundaries: keep `"use client"` on interactive primitives; compose in server components when possible

## Content

- Types: `src/types/content.ts` (`Project`, `BlogPost`, `Writing`)
- Long-form text: `typography.prose` + `max-w-prose`

